.TH WLA\-Z80N 1 "November 2023" "WLA-DX 10.6" "WLA DX Assembler"
.SH NAME
wla\-z80n \- WLA DX cross-assembler for the Zilog Z80N (ZX Spectrum Next)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wla\-z80n
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.B \-o
.I output.o
.I source.asm
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wla\-z80n
assembles Zilog Z80N source code to a WLA DX object file.
The Z80N is an extended Z80 variant with additional instructions used in the ZX Spectrum Next.
.PP
All WLA DX assemblers share an identical command-line interface.
For full option descriptions, examples, and a list of all supported CPU
architectures, see
.BR wla\-6502 (1).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wla\-6502 (1),
.BR wla\-z80 (1),
.BR wlalink (1)
